snippet.title: Fate/Samurai Remnant - Second Trailer
snippet.description:
"Your wish shall perish..." A Holy Grail War begins in Edo Japan.

Fate/Samurai Remnant is scheduled to release September 29, 2023 on Nintendo Switch™, PlayStation®5, PlayStation®4, and Windows PC via Steam®

The "Waxing Moon Ritual", a battle to the death between seven Masters and their Servants to pursue their wishes...

Pre-order now: https://www.koeitecmoamerica.com/fate-sr/?a=products
